      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOST DETERMINED (5) is a talented dog who is a winner of 11 races and filled a minor placing latest when third at this track (20.35). Has a good record here at this journey. Won at his only start from this draw. One of the leading chances. CATCH MY SHADOW (3) was a last start winner (19.99) at this track in a Grade 5 and will jump from box 3 for the first time. Form here sound including five wins. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Should feature again. OPHIDIAN (8) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten a nose into second (20.00) at this track in a Grade 5 over 350m. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Expected to be in this for a long way. BULL MUNDY (1) comes off a (20.20) win last time, scoring by 2.25 lengths in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Loves this draw, having won three of five starts.",
